product.shortDescription: Constructed with durability in mind, this sectional sofa is built to withstand daily use. The high-quality materials ensure long-lasting performance, making it an excellent investment for your living room.
product.description:
Constructed with durability in mind, this sectional sofa is built to withstand daily use. The high-quality materials ensure long-lasting performance, making it an excellent investment for your living room. The plush cushions and chaise lounge provide luxurious comfort, inviting you to unwind and relax after a long day. Experience superior seat comfort with the thick foam padding and ergonomic design. Each seat is designed to provide optimal support and relaxation.

Features:

  • Durable Constructions: Strong square-shaped legs and durable solid wood frame emphasizes the weight load capacity while give this sectional sofa a stylish look.
  • Comfortable Sofa: Skin-friendly polyester upholstery, anti-fade, wrinckle-resist and super soft, combine with high-density sponge cushions.
  • Practical Sectional Sofa: The U-shaped couch is as stylish as it is durable, which blends modern and medieval styles together, matched well with any space.
  • Seat Comfort: The seat cushions are a perfect blend of sponge and spring, providing both thickness and resilience. They remain plush without sagging and offer excellent rebound.
  • Easy to Assemble: Need to be assembled instructions manual and tool included, 3 packages may arrive separately within a few days.

Additions:

  • Inclued: 1 2-seat sofa, 1 single sofa, 1 chaise lounge, 1 ottoman and 4 pillows
  • Product Dimensions: Sofa - 114.3"L x 59.1"W x 33"H.
  • Weight Limit: 1000 lbs, net weight: 186 lbs.

Notes：

  • The size of the product may have slight errors due to manual measurement.
  • The product may be slightly different from the picture due to the light or angle, everything is based on the real thing.
  • If you have any questions please feel free to contact us, contact information can be obtained through the official website customer service.
